description:
With our recent expansion, we are proud to present the results of a collaboration with Perth designer, EUPHOSPUG.

Originally from London and having spent most of his life in Perth, WA, Euphospug has developed a design and illustration style inspired by the skate, rave and science fiction cultures. Euphospug seems to be drawing on the future through layers, movement, style, glitches, digital communication, and visions that never were and may never be .
